    <ui id="config.background.collecting" type="boolean" class="prefer-on tag-glob" data-help="Track new requests originating from browser's background tasks (excluding those originating from extensions). With the default browser config you probably should not disable this as browsers do link pre-fetching in background, and disabling this will miss that data.">Track new requests</ui>
